「'''沒有土地！沒有房屋！不去投票！'''」（[[英文|英文]]：{{lang|en|"'''No Land! No House! No Vote!'''"}}），是[[南非|南非]]許多[[社會運動|社會運動]]的名稱和使用的口號，呼籲如政府不改善貧民的切身問題，就不應參與[[政黨政治|政黨政治]]及[[投票|投票]]<ref>[http://soundzofthesouth.blogspot.com/2011/03/by-voting-we-are-only-choosing-our.html By Voting We Are Only Choosing Our Oppressors] {{Wayback|url=http://soundzofthesouth.blogspot.com/2011/03/by-voting-we-are-only-choosing-our.html |date=20140714223333 }}, Soundz of the South</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
「沒有土地！沒有房屋！不去投票！」的標語最早是為南非的全國性社會組織{{link-en|無土地人民運動|Landless Peoples Movement}}於2004年採用<ref name="#1">{{cite news|url=http://www.abahlali.org/node/865|title="No Vote" Campaigns are not a Rejection of Democracy|publisher=Mail and Guardian|accessdate=2014-07-14|archive-date=2018-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180131200733/http://abahlali.org/node/865/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此運動起初名為「沒有土地！不去投票！運動」（[[英文|英文]]：{{lang|en|''No Land! No Vote!'' campaign}}），組織成員為無土地人民運動及{{le|國家土地委員會|National Land Committee}}（[[英文|英文]]：{{lang|en|National Land Committee}}）。他們認為由於選民必須登記住址才能投票，所以如果人民的產權沒有被保障，他們根本無法投票<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mg.co.za/article/2005-01-25-an-anatomy-of-new-power|title=An anatomy of new power|publisher=Mail and Guardian|accessdate=2014-07-14|archive-date=2014-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724103326/http://mg.co.za/article/2005-01-25-an-anatomy-of-new-power|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]曾報導指有「沒有土地！不去投票！運動」成員在{{link-en|2004年南非大選|South African general election, 2004}}期間受[[酷刑|酷刑]]折磨<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.amnestyusa.org/annualreport.php?id=ar&yr=2005&c=ZAF|title=2005 Annual Report for South Africa|publisher=Amnesty International|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081129162821/http://www.amnestyusa.org/annualreport.php?id=ar&yr=2005&c=ZAF|archivedate=2008-11-29}}</ref>。

2006年，{{link-en|西開普省反迫遷運動|Western Cape Anti-Eviction Campaign}}和{{link-en|棚戶運動|Abahlali baseMjondolo}}加入抵制{{link-en|2006年南非地方政府選舉|South African municipal election, 2006|地方政府選舉}}<ref>[http://secure.financialmail.co.za/06/0217/currents/acurrent.htm Battle to be Heard] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120718071806/http://secure.financialmail.co.za/06/0217/currents/acurrent.htm |date=2012-07-18 }}, by Carol Paton, ''Financial Mail'', 17 February 2006</ref>。西開普省反迫遷運動於選舉日在[[開普敦|開普敦]]舉行遊行，並指他們會投棄權票；棚戶運動又於選舉日遊行，舉出「沒有土地！沒有房屋！不去投票！」的標語，但是次遊行被指是非法，遭到{{link-en|南非警察|South African Police|警方}}鎮壓<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.pambazuka.org/en/category/comment/53204|title=Sekwanele! (Enough is enough!): Post-apartheid land and housing struggles|publisher=Pambazuka|accessdate=2014-07-14|archive-date=2012-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120803053451/http://www.pambazuka.org/en/category/comment/53204|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/>。

2008年，南非社會組織無土地人民運動、西開普省反迫遷運動、棚戶運動和[[農地網絡|農地網絡]]（[[英文|英文]]：{{lang|en|Rural Network}}）組成了{{link-en|貧民聯盟|Poor People's Alliance}}，該聯盟於2009年投票通過抵制[[2009年南非大選|大選]]，並以「沒有土地！沒有房屋！不去投票！」作為標語<ref>[http://www.ainfos.ca/en/ainfos23942.html Resistance Not Ballots; Mass Organisation Not Authoritarian Leaders] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608163041/http://www.ainfos.ca/en/ainfos23942.html |date=2011-06-08 }}, Zabalaza Anarchist Communist Front, 9 May 2010</ref>。該年，參與抵制大選的組織遭受到競選政黨和警方嚴厲的壓制。於2009年2月8日，南非警察被指涉嫌毆打一名抵制大選的居民；警方指他干擾選民登記的進行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://antieviction.org.za/2009/02/09/aec-members-tear-gassed-beaten-and-arrested-residents-lay-blame-on-anc/|title=AEC members tear gassed, beaten and arrested; residents lay blame on ANC|publisher=Anti-Eviction Campaign|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090213234246/http://antieviction.org.za/2009/02/09/aec-members-tear-gassed-beaten-and-arrested-residents-lay-blame-on-anc/|archivedate=2009-02-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://sacsis.org.za/site/article/245.1|title=Elections: A Dangerous Time for Poor People's Movements in South Africa|publisher=SACSIS|access-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110428202117/http://www.sacsis.org.za/site/article/245.1|archive-date=2011-04-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但有說法指這是和他參與貧民聯盟的抵制大選運動有關<ref>{{cite news|url=http://antieviction.org.za/2009/03/03/8-landless-peoples-movement-comrades-under-arrest-in-johannesburg/|title=8 Landless People's Movement Comrades Under Arrest in Johannesburg|publisher=Landless Peoples Movement|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720094540/http://antieviction.org.za/2009/03/03/8-landless-peoples-movement-comrades-under-arrest-in-johannesburg/|archivedate=2011-07-20}}</ref>。

於2011年，其他類似組織，包括無土地人民運動、西開普省反迫遷運動、{{link-en|南非待業人民運動|South African Unemployed Peoples' Movement}}、{{link-en|我們共同成長|Sikhula Sonke}}及{{link-en|曼德拉公園後院之友|Mandela Park Backyarders}}，聯合棚戶運動，呼籲抵制{{link-en|2011年南非地方政府選舉|South African municipal election, 2011|地方政府選舉}}<ref>[http://www.irinnews.org/Report.aspx?ReportId=88883 SOUTH AFRICA: Poor people's movement draws government wrath] {{Wayback|url=http://www.irinnews.org/Report.aspx?ReportId=88883 |date=20100519183108 }}, IRIN,UN Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs, 22 April 2010</ref><ref>[http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/western-cape/w-cape-voters-not-predictable-1.1070406?showComments=true <nowiki>W Cape voters ‘not predictable’</nowiki>] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/western-cape/w-cape-voters-not-predictable-1.1070406?showComments=true |date=20121023141801 }}, Quinton Mtyala and Babalo Ndenze, ''The Cape Argus'', 18 May 2011</ref><ref>[http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/kwazulu-natal/no-land-no-house-no-vote-1.1070896 <nowiki>‘No Land! No House! No Vote!’</nowiki>] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/kwazulu-natal/no-land-no-house-no-vote-1.1070896 |date=20110522152608 }}, ''The Mercury'', By SINEGUGU NDLOVU AND BRONWYN FOURIE, 19 May 2011</ref>。一些地方社區組織也在[[威廉王城|威廉王城]]<ref>[http://www.dispatch.co.za/news/article/1286 <nowiki>We won’t vote for ‘a stranger’</nowiki>] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525124149/http://www.dispatch.co.za/news/article/1286 |date=2011-05-25 }}, Vuvu Vena, ''The Daily Dispatch'', 19 May 2011</ref>、[[菲克斯堡|菲克斯堡]]<ref>[http://mg.co.za/article/2011-05-20-disillusioned-voters-snub-ficksburg-poll/ Disillusioned voters snub Ficksburg poll] {{Wayback|url=http://mg.co.za/article/2011-05-20-disillusioned-voters-snub-ficksburg-poll/ |date=20140715005635 }}, Kwanele Sosibo, ''Mail & Guardian'', 20 May 2011</ref>、[[格拉罕鎮|格拉罕鎮]]<ref>[http://www.ghtnow.co.za/stories/view/unhappy-tantyi-residents-stay-away-from-polls Unhappy Tantyi residents stay away from polls] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120802195913/http://www.ghtnow.co.za/stories/view/unhappy-tantyi-residents-stay-away-from-polls |date=2012-08-02 }} by Thembeni Plaatjie, Grocott's Mail, 20 May 2011</ref>等城鎮舉行了拒絕投票運動。在是次選舉，一共有42%的已登記選民沒有投票<ref>[http://www.businessday.co.za/articles/Content.aspx?id=143490 <nowiki>Elephant will ignore the DA ‘ant’ at its own peril</nowiki>] {{Wayback|url=http://www.businessday.co.za/articles/Content.aspx?id=143490 |date=20120320073745 }}, AUBREY MATSHIQI, ''Business Day'', 23 May 2011</ref>。

== 原因 ==
參與「沒有土地！沒有房屋！不去投票！」運動的人指出有各種理由抵制選舉<ref>[http://sacsis.org.za/site/article/258.1 The Thoroughly Democratic Logic of Refusing to Vote] {{Wayback|url=http://sacsis.org.za/site/article/258.1 |date=20140222225825 }}, SACSIS, 2 April 2009</ref>。他們指出自己自1994年以來均有投票，但至今仍看不到任何積極的結果<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.news24.com/News24/South_Africa/Politics/0,,2-7-12_2452475,00.html|title='No house, no jobs – no vote'|publisher=News24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090301060216/http://www.news24.com/News24/South_Africa/Politics/0,,2-7-12_2452475,00.html|archivedate=2009-03-01}}</ref><ref>[http://newsandletters.org/issues/2011/May-Jun/SAfricaMayJun_11.asp South Africa: 'No Land! No House! No Vote!'] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726081422/http://newsandletters.org/issues/2011/May-Jun/SAfricaMayJun_11.asp |date=2011-07-26 }}, ''News & Letters'', May – June 2011</ref>，而且政客都很腐敗，沒有代表窮人的政黨<ref>[http://mg.co.za/article/2011-04-29-sas-poor-must-shun-the-polls/ SA's poor must shun the polls] {{Wayback|url=http://mg.co.za/article/2011-04-29-sas-poor-must-shun-the-polls/ |date=20140724101606 }}, Andile Mngxitama,''Mail & Guardian'', 2011</ref> 。他們又認為選舉過程本身就是不民主的，窮人應為自己發聲<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.sarpn.org.za/documents/d0002316/Hlongwa_campaign_Feb2007.pdf|title = The No Land, No House, No Vote Campaign Still on for 2009|publisher = SARPN}}{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abahlali.org/node/865|title="No Vote" Campaigns are not a Rejection of Democracy, November 2005|publisher=Abahlali baseMjondolo|accessdate=2014-07-14|archive-date=2018-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180131200733/http://abahlali.org/node/865/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.capetimes.co.za/index.php?fArticleId=4780755|title=Anti Eviction Campaign urges poor to boycott elections |publisher=Cape Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.themercury.co.za/index.php?fArticleId=4882559|title=Apathetic youth a thing of the past |publisher=The Mercury}}</ref><ref>[http://www.pambazuka.org/en/category/comment/71559 <nowiki>The revolt of South Africa’s untouchables</nowiki>] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pambazuka.org/en/category/comment/71559 |date=20140222054053 }}, Pedro Alexis Tabensky, ''Pambazuka'', March 2011</ref>。

== 變種 ==
參與抵制投票的人提出了一些類似的口號，例如「沒有工作！」、「沒有電力！」、「沒有水！」、「沒被尊重！」、「沒有自由！」等，呼籲抵制投票<ref>[http://www.mg.co.za/article/2008-10-30-no-electricity-vote-say-protesters No electricity, no vote, say protesters] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mg.co.za/article/2008-10-30-no-electricity-vote-say-protesters |date=20140724085950 }}, ''Mail & Guardian'', 30 October 2008</ref><ref>[http://www.abahlali.org/node/4406 Devastating Fire in RR Section Khayelitsha – No Electricity! No Vote!] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abahlali.org/node/4406 |date=20140729143014 }}, ''Abahlali.org''</ref><ref>[http://abahlali.org/node/7869 Invitation to All Those Seeking Political Office to Come Down to the People] {{Wayback|url=http://abahlali.org/node/7869 |date=20110324020254 }}, ''Abahlali.org'', 18 March 2011</ref><ref>[http://abahlali.org/node/7868 Abahlali baseMjondolo to March on the KwaZulu/Natal Premier on Human Rights Days] {{Wayback|url=http://abahlali.org/node/7868 |date=20110324020247 }}, ''Abahlali.org'', 18 March 2011</ref>。[[芝加哥反迫遷運動|芝加哥反迫遷運動]]（[[英文|英文]]：{{lang|en|Chicago Anti-Eviction Campaign}}）也使用了類似的口號「沒房屋不投票」（[[英文|英文]]：{{lang|en|"No House No Vote"}}）<ref>[http://inthesetimes.com/uprising/entry/13663/whos_house_our_house_chicago_communities_hold_meeting_to_demand_eviction_mo/ Chicago Communities Demand Eviction Moratorium] {{Wayback|url=http://inthesetimes.com/uprising/entry/13663/whos_house_our_house_chicago_communities_hold_meeting_to_demand_eviction_mo/ |date=20141013005435 }}, by MILES KAMPF-LASSIN, ''In these Times'', 10 August 2012</ref>。

